Talaud Is (Karakelong), Sangihe Is (Sangihe), N 
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFD4F63A80713C66F654F70C" box="[2415,2545,2170,2199]" name="Indonesia" pageId="16" pageNumber="74">Moluccas</collectingCountry>
